id":433931,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你哋唔生,但啲蝻同蝗就生勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多五六年啲小學已經冇曬香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但香港呢個咁嘅生活環境,或者唔生係會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會嘅<br />\n我啲朋友結婚都有共識會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就一定不了"},{"pid":"2c88429dfdb4f87568503d68ca1da6def6ddcef6","tid":433931,"uid":17876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"香港已經唔適合人類居住架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7b48c8453ea5954ee9a995fa2f0eedef514984","tid":433931,"uid":85253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"唔生 何必要佢受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚俾大陸人溝淡？全香港女人一齊生都唔夠蝗蟲嚟啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5948ea3a66d42f1266a78f1c0e4852e2077223b","tid":433931,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔生 何必要佢受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚俾大陸人溝淡？全香港女人一齊生都唔夠蝗蟲嚟啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱 就算全香港一齊生 佢梗有第個幫法對付你<br />\n我寧願呢d痛苦係我呢代快手斷左佢好過"},{"pid":"6a863fff90510c0b3a2e455e1dcdc2b6eda0be63","tid":433931,"uid":48738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"羨慕你地有共識<br />\n我唔想生，但對方想，真係唔知點一齊落去"},{"pid":"05555f596f3042bcde8952304a45cfd43168fd08","tid":433931,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同女朋友有個共識呢世都唔想生<br />\n雖然我都算中產家庭<br />\n搵得都唔算少 但都係生命值換番黎<br />\n但唔想我下一代同我一樣係呢個地方<br />\n日日用晒d時間番工 <br />\n為左發展自己興趣要付出咁大代價<br />\n人生多過一半時間做d唔鍾意嘅野做乜<br />\n不如冇出現過仲好<br />\n如果可以我都想quit game<br />\n<br />\n有預感我屋企過幾年實煩到仆街叫我結婚生仔</blockquote><br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0d34ee25a1cc5dada2c6a630b9f46244e30222","tid":433931,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你哋唔生,但啲蝻同蝗就生勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多五六年啲小學已經冇曬香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但香港呢個咁嘅生活環境,或者唔生係會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔忍心見到本土香港人愈來愈少<br />\n但我想像到下一代會俾我受更多苦"}]}